title: [Cervidae Corral]
description: Bright blue, green, and red canopies stretch across a slender corridor created between the various corrals that stretch across the mixed grass and sedge ground.  Shepherd's crooks are bolted to the tall posts that flank a copper and oak gate, the lanterns dangling from them dormant for the moment.
